<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>.. أَشِدَّاءُ لِدَفْعِ الْبَأْسِ مِنْ كُلِّ بَاسِلٍ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>وَمِنْ كُلَّ قَرْمٍ بِالأَسِنَّةِ لاعِبِ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>تَوَارُثُ إِقْدَامًا وَنُبْلاً وَجُرْأَةً<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>نُفُوسُهُمْ مِنْ أُمَّهَاتٍ نَجَائِبِ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>جَزَى اللهُ أَصْحَابَ النَّبِيِّ مُحَمَّدٍ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>جَمِيعًا كَمَا كَانُوا لَهُ خَيْرَ صَاحِبِ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>وَآلُ رَسُولِ اللهِ لا زَالَ أَمْرُهُمْ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>قَوِيمًا عَلَى إِرْغَامِ أَنْفِ النَّوَاصِبِ<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>ثَلاثُ خِصَالٍ منْ تَعَاجِيبِ رَبِّنَا<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>نَجَابَةُ أَعْقَابٍ لِوَالِدِ طَالِبِ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>خِلافَةُ عَبَّاسٍ وَدِينِ نَبِيِّنَا<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>تَزَايدَ فِي الأَقْطَارِ مِنْ كُلِّ جَانِبِ<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>يُؤيِّدُ دِينَ اللهِ فِي كُلِّ دَوْرَةٍ<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>عَصَائِبُ تَتْلُو مِثْلَهَا مِنْ عَصَائِبِ<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>فَمِنْهُمْ رِجَالٌ يَدْفَعُونَ عَدُوَّهُمْ<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>بِسُمْرِ الْقَنَا وَالْمُرْهَفَاتِ الْقَوَاضِبِ<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>وَمِنْهُمْ رِجَالٌ يَغْلِبُونَ عَدُوَّهُمْ<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>بِأَقْوَى دَلِيلٍ مُفْحِمٍ لِلْمُغَاضِبِ<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>وَمِنْهُمْ رِجَالٌ بَيَّنُوا شَرْعَ رَبِّنَا<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>وَمَا كَانَ فِيهِ مِنْ حَرَامٍ وَوَاجِبِ<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>وَمِنْهُمْ رِجَالٌ يَدْرُسُونَ كِتَابَهُ<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>